==Russian==

===Noun===
'''губа''' (gubá) {{f}}

#[[lip]]
#[[bay]], [[inlet]] (''usually in northern Russia'')
#(''[[military|mil.]]'') a [[stockade]] (''prison'')
#(''[[military|mil.]]'') [[detention]] in a [[stockade]] as a [[punishment]]
#:{{RUchar|[[сажать|сажа́ть]] ''or'' [[отправлять|отправля́ть]] [[на]] губу́}}&nbsp;— ''to [[confine]] to [[stockade]]''

====Declension====
{{ru-noun|губа́|гу́бы|губе́|губу́|губо́й|о губе́|гу́бы|губ|губа́м|гу́бы|губа́ми|о губа́х}}

====Usage====
*Obsolete pronunciation ''gúba'' (meaning ''lip'') is still sometimes preserved in the phrase ''у вас губа не дура'' (see [[#Idioms|Idioms]]).

====Idioms====
